{"tid":1333513,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"流水社運與空間重奪","createTime":"2019-07-19T17:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T17:41:46.000Z","uid":131268,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d162f9df732bc93840719ff5f25adc04f5f9c5ea","tid":1333513,"uid":131268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">//流水社運與空間重奪。今晚有去看<span style=\"color: gold;\">新城市廣場</span>的連儂場，開始有屋邨街坊坐在商場欄杆後面的台階閒聊，與來客談論時事。其他人也是閒閒散散聚集。管理公司不敢滋擾人，因為揭發了<ins>商場地下及二樓原來是二十四小時公共通道</ins>。沙田新市場廣場回復了03年自由行、新裝修之前的親民氣象。這就是左翼一直講的公共空間重奪。<br />\n至於<span style=\"color: blue;\">大埔火車站的隧道</span>，也意外成為長期的民主言論場地。那些<ins>免費取用的貼紙和筆</ins>，更有無政府主義的共享風格。<br />\n流水社運的民主效果，遠遠比大家想像的大得多。首先，是嚇退了公共空間的過分管理（managerialism）。流水社運其實是香港難得一見的民權運動，值得全民繼續參加。（我這個題目的學術深度，足夠寫一篇社會學碩士論文。好快會有人寫。）// #陳雲</span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZJWfzH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZJWfzH.jpg&h=6bac0f01&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZpcLTmn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpcLTmn.jpg&h=415a1ec2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ksk2a77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsk2a77.jpg&h=8ebaca64&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DfPna77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDfPna77.jpg&h=6619b6b2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有份起牆, 我用腦睇字, 我很勁, 你篇論文我有份<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我冇份起牆, 我唔識字, 我手賤"},{"pid":"a047743a7ffbe9c79f525e54d58c17c558343f17","tid":1333513,"uid":207904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"有冇人入嚟一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［戰略分析］香城Online攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333460\" data-a